66const OptionSet<WebsiteDataType>& WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::monitoredDataTypes()
67{
68 static NeverDestroyed<OptionSet<WebsiteDataType>> dataTypes(std::initializer_list<WebsiteDataType>({
69 WebsiteDataType::Cookies,
70 WebsiteDataType::DOMCache,
71 WebsiteDataType::IndexedDBDatabases,
72 WebsiteDataType::LocalStorage,
73 WebsiteDataType::MediaKeys,
74 WebsiteDataType::OfflineWebApplicationCache,
75#if ENABLE(NETSCAPE_PLUGIN_API)

85 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
86

149static Ref<WorkQueue> sharedStatisticsQueue()
150{

155WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore(NetworkSession& networkSession, const String& resourceLoadStatisticsDirectory, ShouldIncludeLocalhost shouldIncludeLocalhost, ResourceLoadStatistics::IsEphemeral isEphemeral)
156 : m_networkSession(makeWeakPtr(networkSession))
157 , m_statisticsQueue(sharedStatisticsQueue())
158 , m_dailyTasksTimer(RunLoop::main(), this, &WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::performDailyTasks)
159 , m_isEphemeral(isEphemeral)
160{
161 RELEASE_ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
162
163 // No daily tasks needed for ephemeral sessions since no resource load statistics are collected.
164 if (isEphemeral == ResourceLoadStatistics::IsEphemeral::Yes)
165 return;
166
167 if (!resourceLoadStatisticsDirectory.isEmpty()) {
168 postTask([this, resourceLoadStatisticsDirectory = resourceLoadStatisticsDirectory.isolatedCopy(), shouldIncludeLocalhost, sessionID = networkSession.sessionID()] {
169 m_statisticsStore = makeUnique<ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore>(*this, m_statisticsQueue, shouldIncludeLocalhost, resourceLoadStatisticsDirectory, sessionID);
170
171 auto memoryStore = makeUnique<ResourceLoadStatisticsMemoryStore>(*this, m_statisticsQueue, shouldIncludeLocalhost);
172 downcast<ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore>(*m_statisticsStore.get()).populateFromMemoryStore(*memoryStore);
173
174 auto legacyPlistFilePath = FileSystem::pathByAppendingComponent(resourceLoadStatisticsDirectory, "full_browsing_session_resourceLog.plist");
175 if (FileSystem::fileExists(legacyPlistFilePath))
176 FileSystem::deleteFile(legacyPlistFilePath);
177
178 m_statisticsStore->didCreateNetworkProcess();
179 });
180
181 m_dailyTasksTimer.startRepeating(24_h);
182 }
183}

185WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::~WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore()

187 RELEASE_ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
188 RELEASE_ASSERT(!m_statisticsStore);
189}

196void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::didDestroyNetworkSession(CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
197{
198 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
199
200 auto callbackAggregator = CallbackAggregator::create([completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] () mutable {
201 completionHandler();
202 });
203
204 m_networkSession = nullptr;
205 destroyResourceLoadStatisticsStore([callbackAggregator] { });
206}

208inline void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::postTask(WTF::Function<void()>&& task)
209{
210 // Resource load statistics should not be captured for ephemeral sessions.
211 RELEASE_ASSERT(!isEphemeral());
212
213 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
214 m_statisticsQueue->dispatch([protectedThis = makeRef(*this), task = WTFMove(task)] {
215 task();
216 });
217}
218
219inline void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::postTaskReply(WTF::Function<void()>&& reply)
220{
221 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
222 RunLoop::main().dispatch(WTFMove(reply));
223}

225void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::destroyResourceLoadStatisticsStore(CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
226{
227 RELEASE_ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
228
229 if (isEphemeral()) {
230 completionHandler();
231 return;
232 }
233
234 postTask([this, protectedThis = makeRef(*this), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
235 m_statisticsStore = nullptr;
236 postTaskReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
237 });

240void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::populateMemoryStoreFromDisk(CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
241{
242 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
243
244 postTask([this, protectedThis = makeRef(*this), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
245 if (m_statisticsStore && is<ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore>(*m_statisticsStore)) {
246 auto& databaseStore = downcast<ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore>(*m_statisticsStore);
247 if (databaseStore.isNewResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseFile()) {
248 m_statisticsStore->grandfatherExistingWebsiteData([protectedThis = WTFMove(protectedThis), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
249 postTaskReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
250 });
251 databaseStore.setIsNewResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseFile(false);
252 } else
253 postTaskReply([this, protectedThis = WTFMove(protectedThis), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
254 logTestingEvent("PopulatedWithoutGrandfathering"_s);
255 completionHandler();
256 });
257 } else
258 postTaskReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
259 });
260}

310void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::statisticsDatabaseHasAllTables(CompletionHandler<void(bool)>&& completionHandler)
311{
312 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
313
314 postTask([this, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
315 if (!m_statisticsStore || !is<ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore>(*m_statisticsStore)) {
316 completionHandler(false);
317 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
318 return;
319 }
320 auto missingTables = downcast<ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore>(*m_statisticsStore).checkForMissingTablesInSchema();
321 postTaskReply([hasAllTables = missingTables ? false : true, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] () mutable {
322 completionHandler(hasAllTables);
323 });
324 });

344void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::resourceLoadStatisticsUpdated(Vector<ResourceLoadStatistics>&& statistics, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
345{
346 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
347
348 // It is safe to move the origins to the background queue without isolated copy here because this is an r-value
349 // coming from IPC. ResourceLoadStatistics only contains strings which are safe to move to other threads as long
350 // as nobody on this thread holds a reference to those strings.
351 postTask([this, protectedThis = makeRef(*this), statistics = WTFMove(statistics), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
352 if (!m_statisticsStore) {
353 postTaskReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
354 return;
355 }
356
357#if ASSERT_ENABLED
358 {
359 Locker stateLocker { suspendedStateLock };
360 ASSERT(suspendedState != State::Suspended);
361 }
362#endif
363
364 m_statisticsStore->mergeStatistics(WTFMove(statistics));
365 postTaskReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
366 // We can cancel any pending request to process statistics since we're doing it synchronously below.
367 m_statisticsStore->cancelPendingStatisticsProcessingRequest();
368
369 // Fire before processing statistics to propagate user interaction as fast as possible to the network process.
370 m_statisticsStore->updateCookieBlocking([this, protectedThis]() {
371 postTaskReply([this, protectedThis = protectedThis]() {
372 logTestingEvent("Statistics Updated"_s);
373 });
374 });
375 m_statisticsStore->processStatisticsAndDataRecords();
376 });
377}

379void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::hasStorageAccess(const RegistrableDomain& subFrameDomain, const RegistrableDomain& topFrameDomain, std::optional<FrameIdentifier> frameID, PageIdentifier pageID, CompletionHandler<void(bool)>&& completionHandler)
380{
381 ASSERT(subFrameDomain != topFrameDomain);
382 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
383
384 if (isEphemeral())
385 return hasStorageAccessEphemeral(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain, frameID, pageID, WTFMove(completionHandler));
386
387 postTask([this, subFrameDomain = subFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), topFrameDomain = topFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), frameID, pageID, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
388 if (!m_statisticsStore) {
389 postTaskReply([completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
390 completionHandler(false);
391 });
392 return;
393 }
394
395 m_statisticsStore->hasStorageAccess(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain, frameID, pageID, [completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)](bool hasStorageAccess) mutable {
396 postTaskReply([completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), hasStorageAccess]() mutable {
397 completionHandler(hasStorageAccess);
398 });
399 });
400 });
401}

403void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::hasStorageAccessEphemeral(const RegistrableDomain& subFrameDomain, const RegistrableDomain& topFrameDomain, std::optional<FrameIdentifier> frameID, PageIdentifier pageID, CompletionHandler<void(bool)>&& completionHandler)
404{
405 ASSERT(isEphemeral());
406
407 if (m_networkSession) {
408 if (auto* storageSession = m_networkSession->networkStorageSession()) {
409 completionHandler(storageSession->hasStorageAccess(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain, frameID, pageID));
410 return;
411 }
412 }
413 completionHandler(false);
414}

443void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::requestStorageAccess(const RegistrableDomain& subFrameDomain, const RegistrableDomain& topFrameDomain, FrameIdentifier frameID, PageIdentifier webPageID, WebPageProxyIdentifier webPageProxyID, StorageAccessScope scope, CompletionHandler<void(RequestStorageAccessResult)>&& completionHandler)
444{
445 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
446
447 if (subFrameDomain == topFrameDomain) {
448 completionHandler({ StorageAccessWasGranted::Yes, StorageAccessPromptWasShown::No, scope, topFrameDomain, subFrameDomain });
449 return;
450 }
451
452 if (isEphemeral())
453 return requestStorageAccessEphemeral(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain, frameID, webPageID, webPageProxyID, scope, WTFMove(completionHandler));
454
455 auto statusHandler = [this, protectedThis = makeRef(*this), subFrameDomain = subFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), topFrameDomain = topFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), frameID, webPageID, webPageProxyID, scope, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)](StorageAccessStatus status) mutable {
456 switch (status) {
457 case StorageAccessStatus::CannotRequestAccess:
458 completionHandler({ StorageAccessWasGranted::No, StorageAccessPromptWasShown::No, scope, topFrameDomain, subFrameDomain });
459 return;
460 case StorageAccessStatus::RequiresUserPrompt:
461 {
462 if (!m_networkSession)
463 return completionHandler({ StorageAccessWasGranted::No, StorageAccessPromptWasShown::No, scope, topFrameDomain, subFrameDomain });
464
465 CompletionHandler<void(bool)> requestConfirmationCompletionHandler = [this, protectedThis, subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain, frameID, webPageID, scope, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] (bool userDidGrantAccess) mutable {
466 if (userDidGrantAccess)
467 grantStorageAccess(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain, frameID, webPageID, StorageAccessPromptWasShown::Yes, scope, WTFMove(completionHandler));
468 else
469 completionHandler({ StorageAccessWasGranted::No, StorageAccessPromptWasShown::Yes, scope, topFrameDomain, subFrameDomain });
470 };
471 m_networkSession->networkProcess().parentProcessConnection()->sendWithAsyncReply(Messages::NetworkProcessProxy::RequestStorageAccessConfirm(webPageProxyID, frameID, subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain), WTFMove(requestConfirmationCompletionHandler));
472 }
473 return;
474 case StorageAccessStatus::HasAccess:
475 completionHandler({ StorageAccessWasGranted::Yes, StorageAccessPromptWasShown::No, scope, topFrameDomain, subFrameDomain });
476 return;
477 }
478 };
479
480 postTask([this, subFrameDomain = subFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), topFrameDomain = topFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), frameID, webPageID, scope, statusHandler = WTFMove(statusHandler)]() mutable {
481 if (!m_statisticsStore) {
482 postTaskReply([statusHandler = WTFMove(statusHandler)]() mutable {
483 statusHandler(StorageAccessStatus::CannotRequestAccess);
484 });
485 return;
486 }
487
488 m_statisticsStore->requestStorageAccess(WTFMove(subFrameDomain), WTFMove(topFrameDomain), frameID, webPageID, scope, [statusHandler = WTFMove(statusHandler)](StorageAccessStatus status) mutable {
489 postTaskReply([statusHandler = WTFMove(statusHandler), status]() mutable {
490 statusHandler(status);
491 });
492 });
493 });
494}
495
496void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::requestStorageAccessEphemeral(const RegistrableDomain& subFrameDomain, const RegistrableDomain& topFrameDomain, FrameIdentifier frameID, PageIdentifier webPageID, WebPageProxyIdentifier webPageProxyID, StorageAccessScope scope, CompletionHandler<void(RequestStorageAccessResult)>&& completionHandler)
497{
498 ASSERT(isEphemeral());
499
500 if (!m_networkSession || (!m_domainsWithEphemeralUserInteraction.contains(subFrameDomain) && !NetworkStorageSession::canRequestStorageAccessForLoginOrCompatibilityPurposesWithoutPriorUserInteraction(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain)))
501 return completionHandler({ StorageAccessWasGranted::No, StorageAccessPromptWasShown::No, scope, topFrameDomain, subFrameDomain });
502
503 CompletionHandler<void(bool)> requestConfirmationCompletionHandler = [this, protectedThis = makeRef(*this), subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain, frameID, webPageID, scope, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] (bool userDidGrantAccess) mutable {
504 if (userDidGrantAccess)
505 grantStorageAccessEphemeral(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain, frameID, webPageID, StorageAccessPromptWasShown::Yes, scope, WTFMove(completionHandler));
506 else
507 completionHandler({ StorageAccessWasGranted::No, StorageAccessPromptWasShown::Yes, scope, topFrameDomain, subFrameDomain });
508 };
509
510 m_networkSession->networkProcess().parentProcessConnection()->sendWithAsyncReply(Messages::NetworkProcessProxy::RequestStorageAccessConfirm(webPageProxyID, frameID, subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain), WTFMove(requestConfirmationCompletionHandler));
511}

513void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::requestStorageAccessUnderOpener(RegistrableDomain&& domainInNeedOfStorageAccess, PageIdentifier openerPageID, RegistrableDomain&& openerDomain)
514{
515 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
516
517 if (isEphemeral())
518 return requestStorageAccessUnderOpenerEphemeral(WTFMove(domainInNeedOfStorageAccess), openerPageID, WTFMove(openerDomain));
519
520 // It is safe to move the strings to the background queue without isolated copy here because they are r-value references
521 // coming from IPC. Strings which are safe to move to other threads as long as nobody on this thread holds a reference
522 // to those strings.
523 postTask([this, domainInNeedOfStorageAccess = WTFMove(domainInNeedOfStorageAccess), openerPageID, openerDomain = WTFMove(openerDomain)]() mutable {
524 if (m_statisticsStore)
525 m_statisticsStore->requestStorageAccessUnderOpener(WTFMove(domainInNeedOfStorageAccess), openerPageID, WTFMove(openerDomain));
526 });
527}
528
529void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::requestStorageAccessUnderOpenerEphemeral(RegistrableDomain&& domainInNeedOfStorageAccess, PageIdentifier openerPageID, RegistrableDomain&& openerDomain)
530{
531 ASSERT(isEphemeral());
532
533 if (m_networkSession) {
534 if (auto* storageSession = m_networkSession->networkStorageSession())
535 storageSession->grantStorageAccess(WTFMove(domainInNeedOfStorageAccess), WTFMove(openerDomain), std::nullopt, openerPageID);
536 }
537}

539void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::grantStorageAccess(const RegistrableDomain& subFrameDomain, const RegistrableDomain& topFrameDomain, FrameIdentifier frameID, PageIdentifier pageID, StorageAccessPromptWasShown promptWasShown, StorageAccessScope scope, CompletionHandler<void(RequestStorageAccessResult)>&& completionHandler)
540{
541 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
542 postTask([this, subFrameDomain = subFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), topFrameDomain = topFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), frameID, pageID, promptWasShown, scope, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
543 if (!m_statisticsStore) {
544 postTaskReply([subFrameDomain = subFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), topFrameDomain = topFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), promptWasShown, scope, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
545 completionHandler({ StorageAccessWasGranted::No, promptWasShown, scope, topFrameDomain, subFrameDomain });
546 });
547 return;
548 }
549
550 m_statisticsStore->grantStorageAccess(WTFMove(subFrameDomain), WTFMove(topFrameDomain), frameID, pageID, promptWasShown, scope, [subFrameDomain = subFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), topFrameDomain = topFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), promptWasShown, scope, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)](StorageAccessWasGranted wasGrantedAccess) mutable {
551 postTaskReply([subFrameDomain = subFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), topFrameDomain = topFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), wasGrantedAccess, promptWasShown, scope, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
552 completionHandler({ wasGrantedAccess, promptWasShown, scope, topFrameDomain, subFrameDomain });
553 });
554 });
555 });
556}
557
558void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::grantStorageAccessEphemeral(const RegistrableDomain& subFrameDomain, const RegistrableDomain& topFrameDomain, FrameIdentifier frameID, PageIdentifier pageID, StorageAccessPromptWasShown promptWasShown, StorageAccessScope scope, CompletionHandler<void(RequestStorageAccessResult)>&& completionHandler)
559{
560 ASSERT(isEphemeral());
561
562 if (m_networkSession) {
563 if (auto* storageSession = m_networkSession->networkStorageSession()) {
564 storageSession->grantStorageAccess(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain, frameID, pageID);
565 completionHandler({ StorageAccessWasGranted::Yes, promptWasShown, scope, topFrameDomain, subFrameDomain });
566 return;
567 }
568 }
569 completionHandler({ StorageAccessWasGranted::No, promptWasShown, scope, topFrameDomain, subFrameDomain });
570}
571
572StorageAccessWasGranted WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::grantStorageAccessInStorageSession(const RegistrableDomain& resourceDomain, const RegistrableDomain& firstPartyDomain, std::optional<FrameIdentifier> frameID, PageIdentifier pageID, StorageAccessScope scope)
573{
574 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
575
576 bool isStorageGranted = false;
577
578 if (m_networkSession) {
579 if (auto* storageSession = m_networkSession->networkStorageSession()) {
580 storageSession->grantStorageAccess(resourceDomain, firstPartyDomain, (scope == StorageAccessScope::PerFrame ? frameID : std::nullopt), pageID);
581 ASSERT(storageSession->hasStorageAccess(resourceDomain, firstPartyDomain, frameID, pageID));
582 isStorageGranted = true;
583 }
584 }
585
586 return isStorageGranted ? StorageAccessWasGranted::Yes : StorageAccessWasGranted::No;
587}
588
589void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::callGrantStorageAccessHandler(const RegistrableDomain& subFrameDomain, const RegistrableDomain& topFrameDomain, std::optional<FrameIdentifier> frameID, PageIdentifier pageID, StorageAccessScope scope, CompletionHandler<void(StorageAccessWasGranted)>&& completionHandler)
590{
591 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
592

863void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::mergeStatisticForTesting(const RegistrableDomain& domain, const RegistrableDomain& topFrameDomain1, const RegistrableDomain& topFrameDomain2, Seconds lastSeen, bool hadUserInteraction, Seconds mostRecentUserInteraction, bool isGrandfathered, bool isPrevalent, bool isVeryPrevalent, unsigned dataRecordsRemoved, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
864{
865 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
866
867 postTask([this, domain = domain.isolatedCopy(), topFrameDomain1 = topFrameDomain1.isolatedCopy(), topFrameDomain2 = topFrameDomain2.isolatedCopy(), lastSeen, hadUserInteraction, mostRecentUserInteraction, isGrandfathered, isPrevalent, isVeryPrevalent, dataRecordsRemoved, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
868 if (m_statisticsStore) {
869 ResourceLoadStatistics statistic(domain);
870 statistic.lastSeen = WallTime::fromRawSeconds(lastSeen.seconds());
871 statistic.hadUserInteraction = hadUserInteraction;
872 statistic.mostRecentUserInteractionTime = WallTime::fromRawSeconds(mostRecentUserInteraction.seconds());
873 statistic.grandfathered = isGrandfathered;
874 statistic.isPrevalentResource = isPrevalent;
875 statistic.isVeryPrevalentResource = isVeryPrevalent;
876 statistic.dataRecordsRemoved = dataRecordsRemoved;
877
878 HashSet<RegistrableDomain> topFrameDomains;
879
880 if (!topFrameDomain1.isEmpty())
881 topFrameDomains.add(topFrameDomain1);
882
883 if (!topFrameDomain2.isEmpty())
884 topFrameDomains.add(topFrameDomain2);
885
886 statistic.subframeUnderTopFrameDomains = WTFMove(topFrameDomains);
887
888 Vector<ResourceLoadStatistics> statistics;
889 statistics.append(WTFMove(statistic));
890 m_statisticsStore->mergeStatistics(WTFMove(statistics));
891 }
892 postTaskReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
893 });
894}

1140void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::scheduleClearInMemoryAndPersistent(ShouldGrandfatherStatistics shouldGrandfather, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
1141{
1142 if (isEphemeral())
1143 return clearInMemoryEphemeral(WTFMove(completionHandler));
1144
1145 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
1146 postTask([this, protectedThis = makeRef(*this), shouldGrandfather, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
1147 if (!m_statisticsStore) {
1148 if (shouldGrandfather == ShouldGrandfatherStatistics::Yes)
1149 RELEASE_LOG(ResourceLoadStatistics, "WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::scheduleClearInMemoryAndPersistent Before being cleared, m_statisticsStore is null when trying to grandfather data.");
1150
1151 postTaskReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
1152 return;
1153 }
1154
1155 auto callbackAggregator = CallbackAggregator::create([completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] () mutable {
1156 postTaskReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
1157 });
1158
1159 m_statisticsStore->clear([this, protectedThis, shouldGrandfather, callbackAggregator] () mutable {
1160 if (shouldGrandfather == ShouldGrandfatherStatistics::Yes) {
1161 if (m_statisticsStore) {
1162 m_statisticsStore->grandfatherExistingWebsiteData([callbackAggregator = WTFMove(callbackAggregator)]() mutable { });
1163 if (is<ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore>(*m_statisticsStore))
1164 downcast<ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore>(*m_statisticsStore).setIsNewResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseFile(true);
1165 } else
1166 RELEASE_LOG(ResourceLoadStatistics, "WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::scheduleClearInMemoryAndPersistent After being cleared, m_statisticsStore is null when trying to grandfather data.");
1167 }
1168 });
1169
1170 m_statisticsStore->cancelPendingStatisticsProcessingRequest();
1171 });
1172}
1173
1174void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::scheduleClearInMemoryAndPersistent(WallTime modifiedSince, ShouldGrandfatherStatistics shouldGrandfather, CompletionHandler<void()>&& callback)
1175{
1176 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
1177
1178 // For now, be conservative and clear everything regardless of modifiedSince.
1179 UNUSED_PARAM(modifiedSince);
1180 scheduleClearInMemoryAndPersistent(shouldGrandfather, WTFMove(callback));
1181}

1266void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::callUpdatePrevalentDomainsToBlockCookiesForHandler(const RegistrableDomainsToBlockCookiesFor& domainsToBlock, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
1267{
1268 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
1269
1270 if (m_networkSession) {
1271 if (auto* storageSession = m_networkSession->networkStorageSession()) {
1272 storageSession->setPrevalentDomainsToBlockAndDeleteCookiesFor(domainsToBlock.domainsToBlockAndDeleteCookiesFor);
1273 storageSession->setPrevalentDomainsToBlockButKeepCookiesFor(domainsToBlock.domainsToBlockButKeepCookiesFor);
1274 storageSession->setDomainsWithUserInteractionAsFirstParty(domainsToBlock.domainsWithUserInteractionAsFirstParty);
1275 }
1276
1277 HashSet<RegistrableDomain> domainsWithUserInteractionQuirk;
1278 for (auto& domain : domainsToBlock.domainsWithUserInteractionAsFirstParty) {
1279 if (needsUserInteractionQuirk(domain))
1280 domainsWithUserInteractionQuirk.add(domain);
1281 }
1282
1283 if (m_domainsWithUserInteractionQuirk != domainsWithUserInteractionQuirk) {
1284 m_domainsWithUserInteractionQuirk = domainsWithUserInteractionQuirk;
1285 m_networkSession->networkProcess().parentProcessConnection()->send(Messages::NetworkProcessProxy::SetDomainsWithUserInteraction(domainsWithUserInteractionQuirk), 0);
1286 }
1287
1288 HashMap<TopFrameDomain, SubResourceDomain> domainsWithStorageAccessQuirk;
1289 for (auto& firstPartyDomain : domainsToBlock.domainsWithStorageAccess.keys()) {
1290 auto requestingDomain = domainsToBlock.domainsWithStorageAccess.get(firstPartyDomain);
1291 if (NetworkStorageSession::loginDomainMatchesRequestingDomain(firstPartyDomain, requestingDomain))
1292 domainsWithStorageAccessQuirk.add(firstPartyDomain, requestingDomain);
1293 }
1294
1295 if (m_domainsWithCrossPageStorageAccessQuirk != domainsWithStorageAccessQuirk) {
1296 if (m_networkSession) {
1297 if (auto* storageSession = m_networkSession->networkStorageSession())
1298 storageSession->setDomainsWithCrossPageStorageAccess(domainsWithStorageAccessQuirk);
1299 m_networkSession->networkProcess().parentProcessConnection()->sendWithAsyncReply(Messages::NetworkProcessProxy::SetDomainsWithCrossPageStorageAccess(domainsWithStorageAccessQuirk), [this, domainsWithStorageAccessQuirk] () mutable {
1300 m_domainsWithCrossPageStorageAccessQuirk = domainsWithStorageAccessQuirk;
1301 });
1302 }
1303 }
1304 }
1305
1306 completionHandler();
1307}

1455void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::suspend(CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
1456{
1457 CompletionHandlerCallingScope completionHandlerCaller(WTFMove(completionHandler));
1458 Locker stateLocker { suspendedStateLock };
1459 if (suspendedState != State::Running)
1460 return;
1461 suspendedState = State::WillSuspend;
1462
1463 sharedStatisticsQueue()->dispatch([completionHandler = completionHandlerCaller.release()] () mutable {
1464
1465 for (auto& databaseStore : ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::allStores())
1466 databaseStore->interrupt();
1467
1468 Locker stateLocker { suspendedStateLock };
1469 ASSERT(suspendedState != State::Suspended);
1470
1471 if (suspendedState != State::WillSuspend) {
1472 postTaskReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
1473 return;
1474 }
1475
1476 suspendedState = State::Suspended;
1477 postTaskReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
1478
1479 while (suspendedState == State::Suspended)
1480 suspendedStateChangeCondition.wait(suspendedStateLock);
1481 ASSERT(suspendedState != State::Suspended);
1482 });
1483}
1484
1485void WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::resume()
1486{
1487 Locker stateLocker { suspendedStateLock };
1488 auto previousState = suspendedState;
1489 suspendedState = State::Running;
1490 if (previousState == State::Suspended)
1491 suspendedStateChangeCondition.notifyOne();
1492}
